The local packaged flvtool2 contain the same files as the the github one,
except the 'test' dir (28,4MB) and the files '.gitignore', 'flvtool2.exe'
and 'flvtool2.exy'. Trust at your own risk or do it by yourself:

$ wget https://github.com/unnu/flvtool2/archive/master.zip
$ unzip master.zip
$ cd flvtool2-master/
$ rm -rf test/ .gitignore flvtool2.exe flvtool2.exy
$ cd ..
$ mv flvtool2-master flvtool2-1.0.6
$ tar jcvf flvtool2-1.0.6.tar.bz2 flvtool2-1.0.6/

What's the point? 28MB x 25kB :-P